Try to correct this:

``` java
@Column(name=&quot;OFFSET&quot;)
private Long offset;
```

to

``` java
@Column(name=&quot;`OFFSET`&quot;)
private Long offset;
```

As `OFFSET` is [reserved keyword](http://www.h2database.com/html/advanced.html#keywords) you should force Hibernate to quote an identifier in the generated SQL by enclosing the column name in backticks in the mapping document. See [this section](https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/orm/5.4/userguide/html_single/Hibernate_User_Guide.html#mapping-quoted-identifiers) of hibernate documentation.

